    <item>
      <title>马克龙推迟选择总理，缩短调整预算的时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/french-economy-latest-macron-s-pm-pick-delay-cuts-time-to-tweak-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国民议会财政委员会主席表示，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙对任命谁为法国新总理进行了长时间的审议，这限制了议员们对预算做出重大修改的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/french-economy-latest-macron-s-pm-pick-delay-cuts-time-to-tweak-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:25:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两名 Ukrenergo 监事会成员因首席执行官被罢免而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/two-ukrenergo-supervisory-board-members-quit-over-ceo-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰电力公司监事会的两名独立成员宣布辞职，以抗议罢免乌克兰电网运营商负责人的“出于政治动机”的决定，并称此举危及了与欧洲合作伙伴的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/two-ukrenergo-supervisory-board-members-quit-over-ceo-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士河问题给威尔士水务公司带来压力，导致其举债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/welsh-water-seeks-debt-as-thames-water-problems-weigh-on-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管围绕泰晤士水务有限公司的担忧继续困扰着整个行业，但投资者对威尔士水务公司新债务出售的需求仍然超过了 12 亿英镑（15.7 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/welsh-water-seeks-debt-as-thames-water-problems-weigh-on-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:40:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者等待利率线索，新兴市场小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/emerging-markets-edge-lower-with-investors-poised-for-rate-clues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大宗商品价格暴跌，且交易员关注一系列经济数据，这些数据将为美联储的降息路径提供更多线索，新兴市场资产连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/emerging-markets-edge-lower-with-investors-poised-for-rate-clues</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
